harharharhar. you know what? i think imma start LJing again...>=] i don't know whyy but i feel like my HYPER ass self againnn WAHAHAHAHAHA. well. lets see. where to start. WHERE TO BEGIN? hah. well lets keep this short n' to the point then eh? this year-SENIOR YEAR has been CRAZY stressful. CRAZY. no joke. its been the most stressful time of my entire LIFE. hohoho. BUT YOU KNOW WHAT. ALL US SENIORS ARE GETTIN THROUGH IT. i heart friends. i'm gonna say that fricken over n' over again foreverrr <3 even those who just say a mere "hi" along w/ a smile on their face make my day JUST that much better :D WHEEEEEEEE. GOOD STUFF. I HEART EVERYONEEEE. but ya know what? STRESSFUL TIME FOR KRISTIN IS NOW OVER. STARTING NOW. i am going to look at life at how i used to look at it. HAPPYYYY N' STRESS FREEE :D i like that much better. harhar. instead of lookin down, LOOK UP. tackle one struggle at a time. i think i like..n' everyone else likes the OPTIMISTIC kristin better than the PESSIMISTIC kristin. foshizzle =D everyone needs to smile more, don't you agree? =D well enough of thisssss harhar. >=] my xmas was pretty awesome. seeing cousins make me smile =D gambling. oh man. we crazyyy kids. i lost 50 bucks, got it back. then won 32 more bucks from pool =] noiceeee. oh yeah. then spent it on movies n' treating my cuzzos to movie FOOD. popcorn/drinks/candy added up to 20 bucks?! harhar. we got fat. (exorcism of emily rose?) ><... third day of barely ne sleep. man are we asian or what. lmao. who says i'm too old more smores. those were the shittttz. uhh..yeah..they had a TRAMPOLENE!!!! don't ask. lmao. -_____- people do weird ass things when they don't sleep mhmmmmm. girls girls again >=] i love this guy! he wanted to be superman. he failed. so he went into the bootleg industry harharhar suckaaa. he was KNOCKED OUT. BEFORE BREAK! wahaha. heartheart interact buddies!!! oh boy. we are coool. hotstuff becca! jesse, anne, me, ritchie! OH YES VIET BUDDAYSSSS!!!!! ENGLISH CREW >=] seanz0r n' sisison i was planning on shoving this candycane up his nose >=] I LOVE JASMINE CHUNG. <33333 ^future hottie krn model GRACE JEONG BABY T!!! LOVERSSSSS our gov't class is the shiznit. stupid muggers -_____- <3 WHEEEE I HEART FRIENDS =D... oh yeah who those who don't know. i have a myspace >=] http://www.myspace.com/mo0 show some love, yeah? =] I WANT TO GO TO UC SANTA CRUZ. I LOVE U GUYS.

wow. i haven't updated in a LONGGGGGGGG while....WELLL I FEEL LIKE UPDATING NOW! wahahaha. this week was definitely an AWESOME week. man. where to start. BENCHBUILDING. fricken awesome i tell u. SOOO SOSOSOSO FUNNN. hahaha. paint wars. food. more paint wars. EVEN THOUGH WE DIDN'T DO WELL IN BENCH...i bet the seniors had the best time making it =] but hey, DOUBLE CROWN BABY!!!! LMAO. OH YEAH! kevin + jennifer and the "looove" hahaha =] HECKAAA CUTE. afterwards jasmine, kevin, jo and i went to pacific commons to find some stuff for "safety day" lol we didnt' find ANYTHING. ><...HANDCUFFS FOR WHAT...LIKE 5.99. lol this lady was like "you kids know your filthy right?" ><...(we were covered in paint) LMFAO. joanna had a purple leg n' jasmine had a white arm...kevin had like HAND PRINTS all over his pants INCLUDING his butt =P no wonder people were staring at us funny ahahaha. then me n' jo went to find our shirts. TOOK US FOREVER..WE WALKED LIKE FOR HECKA DAYS. WOAH WE WERE MAD SEXY. got to school at FIVE O CLOCK. came in, set up all our bench..lol jupp =]..NASA SPACE SHUTTLE fell over lke 10 times lmao. then RAN to cars and started honking our asses off for like 10 minutes straight in our sexy 06 in the parking lot! <3 connie!!!!!!!!! sorry for running away =[...JUMPED into stina's moving car lmao. got "lost" for 5 mins..then on our way back found them again hahaha. RAN to smart and final..and i mean RAN. alex n' his trumpet...dadada da da daaaaaa....CHARGE!!!! j walked..er...ran..had a break...screamed our heads off some more ran around in the halls where no one was even at the school hahaha..."OH SIXXX OH SIXXXXX!" "WHOS A SENIOR?! YOUR MOM'S A SENIOR!" "OOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO..YES! WE ARE SUPERIOR BY FAR!" "WHO ROCKS THE HOUSE I SAY THE SENIORS ROCK THE HOUSE AND WHEN THE SENIORS ROCK THE HOUSE WE ROCK IT ALL THE WAY DOWNNNNN!" stupid juniors tried to screw up our day..its like.."ok please stop u freaks" lmao..they were just jealous ><...haha not all juniors of course <3 just those select few who tried to screw us over..but they failed...miserably..its like DUDE we're just having fun..thats really all that matters during spirit week..the good times..not who wins =] but i do have to give props..junior spirit WAS a LOT better than last years..GO RICHARD! yup yup..our SKIT AND DANCE OWNED ALL OTHERS LIKE MAD MONKEYS. ohhh MAN! we were AWESOME! lol it was kinda hard to dance though >< we were all HECKA tired from NO SLEEP on wednesday i didn't even eat anything ><..and the gym was HECKAAAA hot..man i was afraid i was gonna pass out..lol..not cuz of not eating..but cuz of SCREAMING so fricken much. hahaha..but seriously...words cannot describe how satisfying this experience was =] it was just pure FUN. sorry these aren't really in order ><..and i forgot to bring my camera on monday =[ SORRY JUNIORS. AW GRACE. becca and grace! its coldddd >< jennie becca connie! RAJ SUCKS AT TAKING PICTURES!!! loll =P dance! lmfao. "what is that???"
